Package: notifysendR
Type: Package
Title: Wraps the notify-send Command for Linux Systems
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Matthew", "Berginski", email = "matthew.berginski@gmail.com",
                role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Matthew Berginski <matthew.berginski@gmail.com>
Description: This package wraps the "notify-send" command used to make 
    notifications appear on the desktop of Linux systems. The package exports 
    only one funciton "notify_send", which operates in the same way as the 
    version available from the command line.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
